This paper deals with cross-modal embeddings that capture temporal interactions between visual and textual data. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computer Science dealing with natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), multimedia (cs.MM), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
